{
  "chapter": "093",
  "title": "韩信卢绾列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "韩王信攻略韩地",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>，是原<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩襄王</span>的庶出<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子，身高<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八尺</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五寸</span>。到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>拥立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国后人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>的时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>都已经先立了王，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国没有后人被立，所以就拥立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国诸位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>中的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">横阳君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王成\">成（韩王成）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>，想用他来安抚<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的旧地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>身死，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王成\">成（韩王成）</span>奔投<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>领兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张良</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span>的身份<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span>服<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国旧地，得到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>，任命他为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国将领，率领他的军队跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span>进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "汉王许信为韩王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沛公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">被立为</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>跟从他进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>，于是劝说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>道：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>把各位将领都<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>在靠近关中的地方，而唯独把大王封到这偏远的地方，这是降级贬谪。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>人，翘首企盼东归，趁他们的锐气向东进发，就可以争夺<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>回师<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三秦</span>后，就答应封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>，先<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>，率兵<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻略</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>地。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "信破郑昌受封韩王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>分封的诸王都去就国后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王成\">成（韩王成）</span>因为没有跟随作战、无功可赏，没有被派去就国，反而被改封为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>去<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻略</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>地，就命从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>游历时的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑昌</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>来抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">攻略</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>地<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀城</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>急速<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郑昌\">昌（郑昌）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郑昌\">昌（郑昌）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>，经常率领<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>军跟随作战。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汉王</span>出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周苛</span>等留守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>。等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，不久逃脱，重归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>又立他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>，终于跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年春</span>，于是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">韩王</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">王</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "徙都马邑降匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年春</span>，皇上认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>有才武，所封之地北边靠近<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巩</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>，南边逼近<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">叶</span>，东边有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span>，都是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>劲兵云集之地，于是下诏把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>迁封到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span>以北，以防备<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人，都城设在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>上书说：\"国境紧靠边境，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>屡次入侵，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>离边塞太远，请允许把都城迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>。\" 皇上允许了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>于是迁治到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>。秋天，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>大规模<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围困</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>多次派使者到<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>那里请求和解。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派兵救援，怀疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>屡次派私使，有二心，派人去责备<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>恐怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，于是与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>相约共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">献给</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "平城之围",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年冬</span>，皇上亲自前往<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">铜鞮</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>的军队，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>杀其将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王喜</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>逃奔<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。他与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白土</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曼丘臣</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>等拥立<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵利</span>为王，重新收集<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>战败散失的兵马，又与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>商议<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>派左右<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">贤王</span>率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀骑</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>等屯驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广武</span>以南，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">交战</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>敌军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追击</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">离石</span>，再次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>又在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">楼烦</span>西北聚集军队，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>命令车骑部队<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>屡次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>退，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军乘胜<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追击</span>北逃之敌，听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代谷</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高皇帝</span>驻在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>，派人侦察<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>，回报说\"可以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">出击</span>\"。皇上于是进至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>。皇上出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白登</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>骑兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围困</span>皇上，皇上于是派人厚赂<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">阏氏</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">阏氏</span>于是劝<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>说：\"如今得到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>地，也还是不能居住；况且两国君主不应相互围困。\" 过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七天（时长）</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>的骑兵稍稍撤退。当时天降大雾，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派人往来传递消息，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人察觉不到。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">护军中尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈平</span>对皇上说：\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>人都是完整的兵力，请令<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">彊弩</span>装上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">两矢</span>向外戒备，缓慢前行突出<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">包围</span>。\" 进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的援兵也到了，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>骑于是解围而去。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>也收兵归还。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>为<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>率兵往来侵扰<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>边境。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "韩信被斩于参合",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>等游说诱误<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年春</span>，原<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>再次与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>骑入驻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">参合</span>，抗拒<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>军。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柴将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>他，给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>写信说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>宽厚仁慈，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>虽然有背叛逃亡的，但只要归来，一律恢复原来的爵位名号，并不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。这是大王所知道的。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>因为战败逃奔<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>，并没有大罪，快快自行归来！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>回信说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>把我从平民之中提拔起来，让我南面称孤，这是我的幸运。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>之役，我不能死节，被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>囚禁，这是一罪。等到敌寇<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">进攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马邑</span>，我不能坚守，以城投降，这是二罪。如今<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>为敌人率兵，与将军争<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一旦（时长）</span>之命，这是三罪。像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：范蠡\">蠡（范蠡）</span>没有一罪，尚且身死逃亡；如今我对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>有三罪，还想在世上求得生存，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>之所以在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国丧命的原因啊。如今我逃匿在山谷之间，早晚向<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>乞食度日，我思念归国，就像瘫痪的人不忘站立，盲人不忘视物一样，只是形势不允许罢了。\" 于是交战。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">柴将军</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">屠</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">参合</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "韩信子孙",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>进入<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>时，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>同行；到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">穨当城</span>，生下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儿子</span>，因此取名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穨当</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>也生了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儿子</span>，取名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩婴\">婴（韩婴）</span>。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">孝文十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穨当</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩婴\">婴（韩婴）</span>率领他们的部众<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穨当</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">弓高侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩婴\">婴（韩婴）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">襄城侯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之军作乱时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">弓高侯</span>战功居<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>之首。侯位传<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>无<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，失去侯位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩婴\">婴（韩婴）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子因不敬罪失去侯位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穨当</span>庶出的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩嫣</span>，受宠而显贵，名声富贵显赫于当世。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩说\">说（韩说）</span>，两次受封，多次担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，最终做到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">案道侯</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩代\">代（韩代）</span>，过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">坐法</span>被处死。后过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩说\">说（韩说）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩曾\">曾（韩曾）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">被任命为</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">龙嵒侯</span>，延续<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩说\">说（韩说）</span>之后。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "卢绾从沛起义",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span>邑人，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>同乡里。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>的父亲与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的父亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太上皇</span>彼此相爱，等到生男孩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>同一天出生，乡里乡亲带着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">羊酒</span>祝贺<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两家</span>。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>长大，一同读书，又彼此相爱。乡里人嘉奖<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两家</span>父辈亲爱，生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>同一天，长大后又相爱，再次用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">羊酒</span>祝贺<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两家</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>是布衣之时，因官事逃匿藏身，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>常随他出入上下。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>初次起兵于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>以宾客身份跟随，入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>后任将军，常任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侍中</span>。跟随向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span>身份常伴左右，出入卧室，衣被饮食赏赐，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>没人敢比肩，即使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">萧（萧何）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曹参\">曹（曹参）</span>等人，也只是因公事受礼遇，至于亲近宠幸，没人比得上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长安侯</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，就是从前的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "卢绾封燕王",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉五年冬</span>，因<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项籍</span>，于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">别将</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘贾</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">临江王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共尉</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>了他。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七月</span>归来，跟随<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>已经<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>中非<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">为王者</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七人</span>。他想封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>为王，怕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>失望。等到<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>，就下诏给诸位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">将相</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，选择<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>中有功者立为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>知道皇上想立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>，都说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">长安侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>常跟随平<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，功劳最多，可以<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封王</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。\" 诏书应允了。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉五年八月</span>，于是立曾经的<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span>中受宠幸没有比得上<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>的。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "卢绾通谋匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉十一年秋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>前往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>的军队，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>也从东北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>敌人。当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>向<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>求救。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>也派他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>出使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，告知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>等军已被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>到了<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>那里，原<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儿子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：臧衍\">衍（臧衍）</span>逃亡在<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>，见了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>说：\"您之所以被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国所看重，是因为您熟悉<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>的事务。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国之所以能长久存在，是因为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>屡次<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，战事连绵未决。如今您替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国想急速消<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>等人，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>等人一旦被灭尽，接下来就轮到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国了，您等也将成为俘虏。您为何不让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国暂缓攻击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，而与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>讲和？这事拖下去，可以长久为王于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>；即使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>有急变，也能借此安身保国。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>认为对，于是私下让<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>帮助<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>等<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>怀疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>勾结<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，上书请求<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭族</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张胜\">胜（张胜）</span>归来，把所作的缘由详细陈述。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>醒悟过来，就假意定别人的罪，脱出<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张胜\">胜（张胜）</span>的家属，让他做<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>的间谍，而暗中派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范齐</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>那里，想让他久逃在外，兵连不决。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "卢绾称病亡入匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">汉十二年</span>，东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">征伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>常率兵驻守<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>。他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">裨将</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>，说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范齐</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>相通谋划。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>派使者召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>称病不去。皇上又派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辟阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">审食其</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵尧</span>前去迎<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>，顺便查问其左右。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>更加恐惧，关门躲藏，对他宠信的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>说：\"不姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>而称王的，只有我和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职·规范：长沙王\">长沙（长沙王）</span>罢了。去年春天，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">灭族</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>，夏天，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>的计谋。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今上</span>有病，把政事委托给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>是妇人，一心要以事端<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀异姓王者及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大功臣</span>。\" 于是就称病不前往。他的左右随从都逃亡躲藏。这话颇有泄露，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">辟阳侯</span>听到后，归来将详情报告皇上，皇上更加愤怒。又得到<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>的降者，降者说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张胜</span>逃亡在<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国的使者。于是皇上说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>果然<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>了！\" 派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>率领他全部宫人家属骑兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千</span>住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长城</span>下，观望等待，希望皇上病愈，亲自入朝谢罪。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>于是率领他的部众逃入<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东胡卢王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢绾\">绾（卢绾）</span>被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>欺凌侵夺，常想重归故土。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，死在<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>地。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "绾妻子归汉",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">高后时</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>逃亡<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，正逢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span>生病，不能接见，安置在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">燕邸</span>，准备设酒接见。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>最终驾崩，无缘相见。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>也病死了。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "卢他之封亚谷侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">孝景中六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：卢他之\">他之（卢他之）</span>，以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东胡王</span>身份<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span>，被封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亚谷侯</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "陈豨任边将",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛朐</span>人，不知最初是怎样跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>的。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">高祖七年冬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩王信</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，逃入<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，皇上到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>回来后，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>，让他以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>的身份统领监督<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的边兵，边兵都归他统属。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "陈豨宾客之盛",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>曾经告假归乡，路过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>跟随的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀乘</span>的车马，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>的官舍都住满了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>对待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>以布衣之交，都肯屈居客下。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>返回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>就求入朝见皇上。见了皇上，详细说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>宾客极多，在外掌兵<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>，恐有变乱。皇上于是派人追查<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>客居在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的各种不法之事，多有牵连<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>恐惧，暗中派客人与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曼丘臣</span>处勾通。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">高祖十年七月</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太上皇</span>驾崩，派人召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>声称病重。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九月</span>，于是与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>等<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">劫</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "高祖亲征邯郸",
      "text": "皇上听到后，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>被<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>胁迫<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">劫</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">略</span>的吏民，都<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>了他们。皇上亲自前往，到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，欣喜地说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>不向南占据<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漳水</span>，向北扼守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，我知道他成不了气候。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>奏请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>，说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>二十五城，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，失去了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十城</span>。\" 皇上问：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>是否<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>了？\" 回答说：\"没有<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>。\" 皇上说：\"这是力量不足。\" <span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦免</span>他们，仍任命他们为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>。皇上问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国也有可以做将领的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>吗？\" 回答说：\"有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>。\" <span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>前来拜见，皇上漫骂说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">竖子</span>能做将领吗？\" <span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>惭愧地伏在地上。皇上封给他们各<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千户</span>，任命为将。左右谏道：\"他们跟随入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，功劳未遍赏，如今这些人有何功而加封？\" 皇上说：\"这不是你们所能了解的！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反叛</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>以北都归<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>所有，我用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">羽檄</span>征调<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的兵，没有到来的，如今只有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>城中的兵罢了。我何必吝惜<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四千户</span>封<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四人</span>，不来慰藉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子弟</span>！\" 都说：\"好。\" 于是皇上问：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>以谁为将？\" 回答：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曼丘臣</span>，都是从前的商贾。\" 皇上说：\"我知道了。\" 于是各以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>悬赏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王黄\">黄（王黄）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：曼丘臣\">臣（曼丘臣）</span>等人。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "破豨于曲逆聊城",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年冬</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>的将领<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">侯敞</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">曲逆</span>城下，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>的将领<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张春</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊城</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周勃\">勃（周勃）</span>进军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">平定</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>地。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二月</span>，皇上亲自<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东垣</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东垣</span>未能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻下</span>，士卒辱骂皇上；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东垣</span>投降后，辱骂者被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>，未辱骂者被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">黥</span>刑。改<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东垣</span>名为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">真定</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王黄</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曼丘臣</span>被其部下贪图赏金捕获，都是活捉的，因此<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>的军队于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>亡。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "立恒为代王",
      "text": "皇上还师到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>。皇上说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>位于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>之北，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>却从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山南</span>统辖它，距离太远。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儿子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘恒\">恆（刘恒）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代王</span>，定都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中都</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雁门</span>都归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "樊哙斩豨于灵丘",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">高祖十二年冬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>的军队终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">追</span>上并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：陈豨\">豨（陈豨）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灵丘</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "太史公论叛臣",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">韩信（韩王信）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>并非世代积德行善之家，他们侥幸利用一时权变，以诈力成功，正赶上<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝初<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">定</span>，所以得以裂土封疆，南面称孤。内心因势力强大而被猜疑，对外依靠<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮貊</span>作为援助，因此日渐疏远，自身危险，事穷智困，终于投奔<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，难道不令人悲哀吗！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地人，他年少时多次称赞仰慕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：信陵君\">魏公子（信陵君）</span>；等到担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>守边，招致<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>礼贤下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，名声超过实际。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周昌</span>怀疑他，瑕疵颇多生起，他怕祸及自身，奸邪之人又来进说，终于陷入无道之境。唉，真是悲哀！谋划的生熟对人的成败影响何其深远啊！"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩襄王\">韩襄（韩襄王）</span>的遗孽，最初随军从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉中</span>兴起。 <span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>南面称王，迁邑北通胡地。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">穨当</span>归国受封，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩说\">龙雒（韩说）</span>立有战功。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卢绾</span>受亲爱宠幸，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>无人能比。 旧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地受封为王，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">东胡</span>之计穷尽。"
    }
  }
}